title: CFB Week 10 Fall Out
description:
Wendi Nix, Desmond Howard, Rod Gilmore, and Heather Dinich take a look at the results from Week 10 in the College Football landscape. The crew also gets prepared for the second CFP Rankings results and how this past weekend's action had an impact on those rankings.
